{"data":[{"id":564152378,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2df7e977a7b55bf0851cbd3c7f991478","url_token":"loveczerny","name":"伟大的车尔尼","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/99e737e15c8f720821bc23c33ad3f591_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/99e737e15c8f720821bc23c33ad3f591_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2df7e977a7b55bf0851cbd3c7f991478","user_type":"people","headline":"爱好计算机和音乐，崇拜车尔尼。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1725,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564152378","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546335715,"updated_time":1546340190,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e首先作一些说明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1、本回答中都使用文字描述，不使用符号描述。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2、由于集合B就是哥德巴赫猜想本身，因此考虑集合A是去掉集合B的部分，即集合A是这样的集合，其中的每一个元素都是正偶数且可以表示成一个正质数和一个负质数的和。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后回答证明有什么错误。错误还不止一处。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e临时定义-1负质数本身是没有问题的，数学证明过程中经常出现临时定义新的概念。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样哥德巴赫猜想变式一二三都可以改写成如下描述：任意正偶数属于集合B或集合A（根据上面的说明，集合A和集合B的交集为空）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e主要考虑哥德巴赫猜想变式一的错误，另外两个变式的错误是类似的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问题出在这个命题上：若-1是质数，则任意正偶数属于集合A。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个命题的逆否命题：若存在正偶数不属于集合A，则-1不是质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e根据集合A的定义，-1必须是负质数。因此原命题的条件必须为真，逆否命题的结论必须为假。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么原命题的结论“任意正偶数属于集合A”是否为真？答案是否定的。例如8=9+(-1)就不满足这一点，9是合数，因此原命题的结论为假，逆否命题的结论为真，原命题和逆否命题都是假命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使将集合A的范围增大，即把集合B作为集合A的子集，看似哥德巴赫变式一找不到反例，但是相当于什么也没证明，只是引入了“负质数”这个新概念，将“质数”的范围扩大，从已知的推出已知的，没有任何有效证明，因此根本没有证明哥德巴赫猜想变式一是真命题，同理也没有证明哥德巴赫猜想变式二和三是真命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使将集合A的范围增大以后证明了哥德巴赫猜想变式一二三都是真命题（其实那个证明连这一点都没有做到），也不能由集合A推出集合B，因为集合B是集合A的子集，只能由子集推出超集而不能由超集推出子集。典型的例子有，如果一个人是中国人那么这个人一定是亚洲人，但是反过来不成立，如果一个人是亚洲人并不能推出这个人是中国人，因为亚洲有很多国家。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"首先作一些说明。1、本回答中都使用文字描述，不使用符号描述。2、由于集合B就是哥德巴赫猜想本身，因此考虑集合A是去掉集合B的部分，即集合A是这样的集合，其中的每一个元素都是正偶数且可以表示成一个正质数和一个负质数的和。然后回答证明有什么错误。错…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=150\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_de